\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Oddness with his blood. Indicates that he isn\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92t commited. -swirls it around a bowl to check the body, the thickness, how many drips fell down the side of the bowl. Elrahet-  \u8220\'93His blood is thin but sharp.}}